    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_d4565fd9"><bpmn:text>Check exception in Art. 18 Abs. 1 lit. b&#10;Check exception in Art. 18 Abs. 1 lit. c&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: Data is Accurate AND Limit</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_365282e2"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: Processing Was Lawful AND Limit</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_d7785c3c"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: LegalClaim</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_66bcf6f1"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 21 Abs. 1&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: Permitted AND Consent Withdrawn AND Legitimate Interest AND High Risk to Individuals</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_32eaa78f"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: Limit AND Original Consent Given AND Data Subject Gave Consent AND LegalClaim</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_8c6a3b1b"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: Limit</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
